Package org.eclipse.collections.impl.stack.mutable.primitive

Class CharArrayStack

java.lang.Object
org.eclipse.collections.impl.stack.primitive.AbstractCharStack
org.eclipse.collections.impl.stack.mutable.primitive.CharArrayStack
All Implemented Interfaces:
Externalizable, Serializable, CharIterable, OrderedCharIterable, PrimitiveIterable, CharStack, MutableCharStack
public class CharArrayStack
extends AbstractCharStack
implements MutableCharStack, Externalizable
CharArrayStack is similar to ArrayStack, and is memory-optimized for char primitives. This file was automatically generated from template file primitiveArrayStack.stg.
